{"seq": 775, "ts": "2026-05-17T12:36:43Z", "op": "upsert", "record_id": "REQ-264", "record": {"id": "REQ-264", "kind": "requirement", "status": "active", "label": "HF Leaderboard Rate-Limit Handling", "confidence": 0.7, "source_type": "observed", "evidence": ["synced from requirements.json"], "epistemic_boundary": [], "is_hypothesis": false, "model_assumptions": {}, "recursion_depth": 0, "data": {"id": "REQ-264", "title": "HF Leaderboard Rate-Limit Handling", "description": "The HF leaderboard sync MUST handle HTTP 429 with exponential-backoff retry (up to 4 attempts). It MUST parse the `RateLimit: \"api\";r=X;t=Y` header to extract the exact reset window and wait accordingly. A +1 s safety margin MUST be added to the `t=` value.", "source": "ARCHITECTURE.md §21 [HF-002]", "status": "implemented"}}, "prev_hash": "22481c3a7dd719e1a9ebcc496343102605fbd5efec4bafa75610507468a07a28", "hash": "1e5f4a3b12ffa3260249358f34582cb68f0fa4af654399c667d916479ec78e2b", "recursion_depth": 0}
{"seq": 776, "ts": "2026-05-17T12:36:43Z", "op": "upsert", "record_id": "REQ-265", "record": {"id": "REQ-265", "kind": "requirement", "status": "active", "label": "HF API Token Support", "confidence": 0.7, "source_type": "observed", "evidence": ["synced from requirements.json"], "epistemic_boundary": [], "is_hypothesis": false, "model_assumptions": {}, "recursion_depth": 0, "data": {"id": "REQ-265", "title": "HF API Token Support", "description": "When `SPECSMITH_HF_TOKEN` or `hf_api_token` is configured, the HF sync MUST include an `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header. The CLI `specsmith model-intel test-hf` MUST validate the token via `huggingface.co/api/whoami-v2` and report whether the Datasets Server is reachable.", "source": "ARCHITECTURE.md §21 [HF-003]", "status": "implemented"}}, "prev_hash": "1e5f4a3b12ffa3260249358f34582cb68f0fa4af654399c667d916479ec78e2b", "hash": "3a78789f5e8a9364ff53c6767beb12f26606cf61da601827a06263fbfd7c20a5", "recursion_depth": 0}
{"seq": 777, "ts": "2026-05-17T12:36:43Z", "op": "upsert", "record_id": "REQ-266", "record": {"id": "REQ-266", "kind": "requirement", "status": "active", "label": "HF Leaderboard Static Fallback", "confidence": 0.7, "source_type": "observed", "evidence": ["synced from requirements.json"], "epistemic_boundary": [], "is_hypothesis": false, "model_assumptions": {}, "recursion_depth": 0, "data": {"id": "REQ-266", "title": "HF Leaderboard Static Fallback", "description": "When HF is unreachable (network error, 5xx, or zero parseable rows), specsmith MUST load built-in static benchmark scores covering at least 40 models (OpenAI GPT-4o/mini, Claude 3.5 sonnet/haiku, Gemini 2.x, Mistral, Qwen, Llama, DeepSeek, Phi). The fallback MUST be transparent to callers.", "source": "ARCHITECTURE.md §21 [HF-004]", "status": "implemented"}}, "prev_hash": "3a78789f5e8a9364ff53c6767beb12f26606cf61da601827a06263fbfd7c20a5", "hash": "683793f8d128a12cd105fd668b4a4b9d6ed6c4ec5f8fbd5bb6394cf0841c75ba", "recursion_depth": 0}
{"seq": 778, "ts": "2026-05-17T12:36:43Z", "op": "upsert", "record_id": "REQ-267", "record": {"id": "REQ-267", "kind": "requirement", "status": "active", "label": "Bucket Scoring Engine", "confidence": 0.7, "source_type": "observed", "evidence": ["synced from requirements.json"], "epistemic_boundary": [], "is_hypothesis": false, "model_assumptions": {}, "recursion_depth": 0, "data": {"id": "REQ-267", "title": "Bucket Scoring Engine", "description": "specsmith MUST compute three task-bucket scores from raw benchmark values (0–100 scale): Reasoning = 0.35×MATH + 0.30×GPQA + 0.25×BBH + 0.10×IFEval; Conversational = 0.40×IFEval + 0.35×MMLU-PRO + 0.25×BBH; Longform = 0.35×MUSR + 0.35×IFEval + 0.30×MMLU-PRO. Scores MUST be rounded to 2 decimal places.", "source": "ARCHITECTURE.md §22 [BKT-001]", "status": "implemented"}}, "prev_hash": "683793f8d128a12cd105fd668b4a4b9d6ed6c4ec5f8fbd5bb6394cf0841c75ba", "hash": "1b384fe0f430dd1ffe9a726dadc3d16105c5319d46f2b61df7c454fdad4adbc3", "recursion_depth": 0}
{"seq": 779, "ts": "2026-05-17T12:36:43Z", "op": "upsert", "record_id": "REQ-268", "record": {"id": "REQ-268", "kind": "requirement", "status": "active", "label": "Model Intelligence Recommendations", "confidence": 0.7, "source_type": "observed", "evidence": ["synced from requirements.json"], "epistemic_boundary": [], "is_hypothesis": false, "model_assumptions": {}, "recursion_depth": 0, "data": {"id": "REQ-268", "title": "Model Intelligence Recommendations", "description": "`specsmith model-intel recommendations [--bucket reasoning|conversational|longform]` MUST return the top-10 models sorted by the requested bucket score. The governance HTTP server MUST expose `GET /api/model-intel/recommendations?bucket=<name>` returning the same data.", "source": "ARCHITECTURE.md §22 [BKT-002]", "status": "implemented"}}, "prev_hash": "1b384fe0f430dd1ffe9a726dadc3d16105c5319d46f2b61df7c454fdad4adbc3", "hash": "acb8059c1718ee547135bb48927688e56a448610f51423bb0706e9ad6ab4e67b", "recursion_depth": 0}
